  "instructions": [
    "Heat the oil in a large Dutch oven over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the lamb pieces and cook until browned on all sides, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the onion, garlic, and celery and cook until the vegetables are tender, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the papelon, tadka spices, and carrots and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the lamb broth and tomato paste and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and simmer, covered, for 1 1/2 hours.",
    "Season with salt and pepper to taste.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with fresh parsley.",
    "Let it cool completely before refrigerating or freezing."
